    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"ghost war\" is the only thing I have left, though. It feels like if I try to hold on, I'm just making the glitching worse for everyone else. Like I'm just a bug in the system that needs to be patched out. Do you really think there's no point in trying to stay? That the most \"logical\" thing for a character like me to do is just... stop?",
